		<div id="unique-entry-id-260" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Twilight Saga</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 29 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-vampires.php">Vampires</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-side-tracked.php">Side Tracked</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ideas/lookalikes/online/online.html" rel="self" title="Online"><img class="imageStyle" alt="mouse" src="mouse.jpg" width="41" height="41" /></a></div>I would like to thank Spiky and my friends on Super Poke Pets and the Twilight Club on SPP, for the almost complete Twilight saga.<br />Please see <a href="../../../twilight/twilight.html" rel="self" title="Twilight Story by SPP">http://www.tempesttwins.co.uk/twilight/twilight.html</a><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-259" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">More Stories Told In Pictures</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Monday, 16 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-vampires.php">Vampires</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-side-tracked.php">Side Tracked</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ideas/lookalikes/online/online.html" rel="self" title="Online"><img class="imageStyle" alt="mouse" src="mouse.jpg" width="41" height="41" /></a></div>I have a virtual pet and have designed several habitats for him.  As the movie New Moon is about to be released, here is the story as told with the help of friends on Super Poke Pets and the Twilight Club on SPP.<br />Please see <a href="../../../ideas/pics/newmoon/newmoon.html" rel="self" title="New Moon">http://www.tempesttwins.co.uk/pics/newmoon/newmoon.html</a><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-258" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">New Way Of Reading</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 13 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><img class="imageStyle" alt="books" src="books.jpg" width="42" height="40" /></div>I have just had an email that sound curious.  Apparently Nintendo DS will soon be releasing the Flips range -- a new series on Nintendo DS designed to give children of all ages a fun new way to read their favourite books (including Artemis Fowl by Eoin Colfer).  Flips uses the DS touch screen and stylus to enable children to read and interact by combining the world of storytelling with quizzes and references to characters.<br /><br />So what does Eoin Colfer think "I'm over the moon to see my stories and characters brought to life on the Nintendo DS with the new FLIPS range.  Everyone knows that reading improves literacy skills. I have two children who are DS fanatics and cannot wait for the FLIPS to arrive, so EA might finally get them reading my books!"<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-257" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Pictures Online.</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 13 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-books.php">Books</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-side-tracked.php">Side Tracked</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="../../../ideas/lookalikes/online/online.html" rel="self" title="Online"><img class="imageStyle" alt="mouse" src="mouse.jpg" width="41" height="41" /></a></div>I have a virtual pet and have designed several habitats for him.  So I thought I would show some of the habitats here and I wondered if the crew may have their own Vampirates work online too.<br />See <a href="../../../ideas/pics/vampirate/vampirate.html" rel="self" title="Vampirates">http://www.tempesttwins.co.uk/pics/vampirates/vampirates.html</a><br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-254" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Addresses</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Monday, 09 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>For those of you looking to send anything to Justin Somper here is the address he gave on his blog a little while ago.<br />"you can send stuff to me c/o Simon & Schuster Children's Books (Publicity), Africa House, 64-78 Kingsway, London WC2B 6AH."<br /><br />Comment: This address is now out of date.  Please see the blog entry dated 1st July 2011 for the correct address.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-256" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">New Blog</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Friday, 06 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>Justin Somper has finally had the chance to sit down and write a new blog for us.  (It was meant to be sent out for halloween but owing to a technical difficulty it has just arrived.)<br />See <a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/vip-page/blog/belatedhappyhalloween/default.aspx" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk">www.vampirates.co.uk</a> to read the new blog.<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-253" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Halloween</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 01 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-pirates.php">Pirates</a></span><span class="blog-entry-category"> <a href="category-side-tracked.php">Side Tracked</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><img class="imageStyle" alt="jolly roger" src="jollyroger.jpg" width="40" height="39" /></div>I hope you had the chance to dress up.<div class="image-right"><img class="imageStyle" alt="" src="page57_blog_entry253_2.jpg" width="67" height="100" /></div><br />You can probably guess what I dressed up as.  (Well without the wig).<br /></div></div><div id="unique-entry-id-252" class="blog-entry"><h1 class="blog-entry-title">Halloween in Holloway</h1><div class="blog-entry-date">Sunday, 01 November 2009 Filed in: <span class="blog-entry-category"><a href="category-justin-somper.php">Justin Somper</a></span></div><div class="blog-entry-body"><div class="image-left"><a href="http://www.vampirates.co.uk/" rel="external" title="www.vampirates.co.uk"><img class="imageStyle" alt="vampirates" src="vampirates.jpg" width="40" height="40" /></a></div>Justin Somper was at Halloween in Holloway yesterday.  It sounded as if it was a good show.<br />See <a href="http://www.therowanartsproject.com/" rel="external" title="http://www.therowanartsproject.com/">www.therowanartsproject.com</a><br /></div></div>
	</div>
	
	 
